      <title>美国批准房地美购买第二笔抵押贷款试点计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/us-approves-freddie-mac-pilot-program-to-buy-second-mortgages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国监管机构已批准房地产巨头房地美（Freddie Mac）开展一项购买二次抵押贷款的试点计划，这一转变最终可能降低家庭以房屋净值作为抵押的贷款成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/us-approves-freddie-mac-pilot-program-to-buy-second-mortgages</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
